      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.hIhgdXnqGHBm0A64]{Envoy Improvisation}</p>\n<p>As a move action, you can cause one ally adjacent to you to not be considered @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.RxvbSB9ZgSCBu2jw]{helpless} (see page 276) for the purpose of actions that can be used only against helpless creatures (such as a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.Fu5eDR99bGo9WdUU#coup-de-grace]{coup de grace}). This effect ends if the creature ceases to be adjacent to you or at the beginning of your next turn, whichever comes first.</p>"
